title: Godsmack *LIVE* Wilkes Barre, PA. (2004)
description:
Godsmack brings down the house with this live concert footage capped for your viewing pleasure. This 1 hour and 4 minute (approx) long concert has some behind the scenes footage as well as live concert hoodwinks. Prepare to have your face BLOWN OUT!

Bandmembers live it up on their "Faceless" tour and show what life on the road is like when your in a heavy metal band. Songs in this set include "Awake", "Faceless", "Bad Religion", "Moon Baby", "Changes", and more.

Song List:

1 Straight Out of Line
2 Awake
3 Faceless
4 Bad Religion
5 Moon Baby
6 Serenity
7 Re-Align
8 Changes
9 Keep
10 Voodoo
11 Batalla de los Tambores
12 Stand Alone
